# Production client build (pnpm --filter @aethelos/client build).
# Peer mailboxes from the desktop app are primary; these are silent fallback only.
#
# WARNING: If both VITE_DEFAULT_RELAY_URL and VITE_BOOTSTRAP_RELAYS stay unset,
# browser-only founders get an empty relay pool until someone publishes a mailbox.
# Uncomment and set real wss:// URLs before hosting a public PWA without desktop founders:
# VITE_DEFAULT_RELAY_URL=wss://relay.yourdomain.org
# VITE_BOOTSTRAP_RELAYS=wss://relay-a.example.org,wss://relay-b.example.org
# VITE_INVITE_BASE_URL=https://app.yourdomain.org
